<refsect1>
<title
>Exemplos</title>
<para
>Executar o <command
>kfmclient</command
> com o usuário <systemitem class="username"
>jose</systemitem
> e mostrar o ícone do &konqueror; na janela de senhas:</para>
<screen
><userinput
>$(kde4-config --path libexec)<command
>kdesu</command
> <option
>-u jose</option
> <option
>-i konqueror</option
> <command
>kfmclient</command
></userinput
></screen>

</refsect1>

